name: Big Brains
description: This is a model I made for creating Big Brained characters. You know that sci-fi trope where they want you to konw that someone is super smart, so they have a huge head to hold their massive brain? That's what this is for.

modelVersions.name: v1
modelVersions.description: I've made a lot of versions of this, but this is the first one I thought was good enough to share with people, so I'm calling it v1.
